    <fullName>Donor_Level__c</fullName>
    <description>Giving level based on Total Gifts and Payments Current FY. 

1.	Only the donation table
2.	Stage = received or pending installment
3.	Record types = Major Gifts, Single Gifts, Recurring Gifts, Grant, Pledge Installment
4.	Close Date = current FY

All amounts from gifts meeting the above criteria are added together to come up with a total. This total is used to determine donor level

The field should be called Total Gifts and Payments Current FY</description>
